items.title: Hassett says Fed independence is ‘really important’ and chair candidates shouldn’t be disqualified for being Trump’s friend
items.description: Hassett declined in a CNBC interview to directly address his own candidacy but said forging consensus is an important part of the job.

items.title: Payrolls rose by 64,000 in November after falling by 105,000 in October, delayed jobs numbers show
items.description: Nonfarm payrolls were expected to increase by 45,000 in November as the unemployment rate rose to 4.5%.

items.title: China lowers anti-dumping tariffs on European pork exporters
items.description: China on Tuesday announced lower duties on pork imports and pig by-products from the European Union.
